HOW THE KYC PROCESS WORKS INTERNALLY

Let‚Äôs break the process into simple steps.

STEP 1 ‚Äî User uploads ID + selfie + liveness video.

Our AI verifies:

Face matches ID

ID is not forged

Video is real human (anti-deepfake)

Document is valid

Nationality + age rules

Sanctions/PEP check

Detect if user used this ID before (duplicate prevention)

STEP 2 ‚Äî We extract ONLY verification results

Example results:

age ‚â• 18

nationality = IN

sanctioned = false

faceMatchScore = 97%

human = true

document validity = true

STEP 3 ‚Äî Zero-Knowledge circuit generates zkProof

A SNARK/STARK circuit encodes:

Verified = true

Age ‚â• 18

Not sanctioned

Human verified

Unique identity

The circuit produces:

proof.hash

publicSignals

This is the ONLY thing sent on-chain.

STEP 4 ‚Äî Mint zkPassport (Soulbound NFT) on Polygon

The NFT stores:

isVerified: true

ageFlag: true

sanctionFlag: false

humanFlag: true

identityHash: <encrypted>

ALL personal data is thrown away.

STEP 5 ‚Äî Link zkPassport to a stealth identity

We use ERC-5564 stealth addresses:

generate a stealth wallet

link the passport to it

user never reveals real identity wallet

no one knows which wallet belongs to which person




